OL,6,FBeverley Griggs, Consultant in Public
OL,7,FHealth for and Chair of the multi-
OL,8,Fagency Incident Management Team, said:
OL,9,F"We are taking this opportunity to
OL,10,Fremind parents that measles cases are
OL,11,Fincreasing in the UK, and that
OL,12,Fchildren should receive two MMR doses
OL,13,Fto give them the best protection
OL,14,Fagainst measles.
OL,16,F"We are investigating two confirmed
OL,17,Fcases of in the Gwent area. As part of
OL,18,Four investigations, we have identified
OL,19,Fa number of patients who attended the
OL,20,FCEAU at Grange Hospital at specific
OL,21,Ftimes between 30 March and 2 April.
