OL,6,F"The parents of these patients will
OL,7,Freceive a text message with a link
OL,8,Fwith further information about what
OL,9,Fthey should look out for in their
OL,10,Fchildren, and what they should do if
OL,11,Fthey have concerns.
OL,13,F"Any contacts who are unimmunised are
OL,14,Fat increased risk of and will be asked
OL,15,Fto stay away from nursery, school or
OL,16,Fchildcare settings for two weeks. This
OL,17,Fis routine public health action and is
OL,18,Fintended to prevent further
OL,19,Ftransmission of the infection.
